Description: Unique hashed identifier from Children Helping Science for a child
Possible values: Unique six character long alphanumeric string

Description: Unique identifier from Project GARDEN for a child, connected to child__hashed_id
Possible values: Unique eight character long alphanumeric string

Description: Age in years at time of response of a participant
Indicator of whether all data should be excluded for a participant
Possible values: 1 = exclude, 0 = include

Description: Explanation for why all data should be excluded for a participant
Possible values: Text explanation when VO_exclude = 1, Blank/NA when VO_exclude = 0

Description: Timestamp for when participant began the session
Percentage of trials a participant answered correctly (accuracy)
Number of trials that a participant completed

Possible values: 1 = correct, 0 = wrong, NA = trial not completed.
